description: You'll be the coolest customer in town when this frozen favorite is slinging sweet treats at your next event. A St. Louis treasure, Frosty Favorites has everything your sweet tooth could ever ask for. Cones, bars, ice pops, ice cream sandwiches, and all in a variety of styles and flavors - this truck truly has it all. Frosty Favorites will bring the greatness you can expect from an ice cream truck in the Gateway to the West, and we just know you and your guests will agree. Don't settle for less than the best, get Frosty Favorites to cater all your most important moments!
name: Frosty Favorites
